<div>
<% if newest_article.main_asset %>
<%= image_tag newest_article.main_asset.galleryitem.url(:thumb) %>
<% end %>
<h1>Our latest published article is '<%= link_to h(newest_article.title), article_path(newest_article) %>'</h1>

<p>The article is from <%= h newest_article.country.title %>, and was <%=
getArticlePublishedDetails(newest_article).downcase %>. The article has <%= newest_article.assets.size %> images

<% if newest_article.comments.empty? %>
but <span class="bold">no</span> comments. <%= link_to 'Be the first to comment on this article', article_path(newest_article) %>!
<% else %>
and <span class="bold"><%= newest_article.comments.size %> comments.
<% end %>

</p>

</div>
